HEADWORD: Mazurka
<hw>Ma*zur"ka</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A Polish dance, or the music
which accompanies it, usually in 3-4 or 3-8 measure, with a strong
accent on the second beat.</def>⟦br⟧
